						               													<description>You will be building and improving your robot as you explore custom spaceships looking for scrap.&amp;#10;Best scrapper wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Game:&amp;#10;Players start out with a basic robot that they then are able to upgrade.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Three rounds are played in each round the player can:&amp;#10;1. Sell items from scrapping or old robot parts.&amp;#10;2. Buy parts and upgrade their robot.&amp;#10;3. Scrap a new ship.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ships are designed by one of the players using the ship cards in the deck and explored with robot shaped pawns. Movement on the ship is based on the robot built, up grade the robot for better movement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How much scrap or the ability to fight off an alien is based  on the level of the robot. Upgrade the robot to not lose in a fight and to bring more treasure home!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The ship has events that happen so staying too long on a ship could cost you your scrap or part of your robot!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To Win:&amp;#10;Players will sell all their scrap and the robots they have built and the player with the most amount of money at the end of the game wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Set comes with poker sized playing cards, money and pawns.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
